name: A Shoot from IPhone
description:
I guess in every music festival or a concert, you'll see someone held their phone up high, capturing their favorite artist doing live performance. For me, it is totally fine. I mean, everyone wanted to record their loved ones, right? And as a photographer myself, I love documenting this kind of photos, I can feel the emotion of them through their cell phone.
-----------
*Shoot in analog camera with Fuji Industrial 400 film
